<h2>OrderingList Demos</h2>

<p>
{{#markdown}}
The orderingList is a widget use to manually sort elements in a list, supporting both a list layout and
a table layout.  It is based on the jQuery UI [sortable](http://jqueryui.com/sortable/) and [selectable](http://jqueryui.com/selectable/)
plugins.
{{/markdown}}
</p>

<h3>OrderingList in List mode:</h3>
<p>A simple orderingList widget with items laid out in list format.  To use the widget, simply invoke the plugin passing
in a reference to the <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> element that identifies your list element.  The widget will create any additional
DOM nodes required to enable user interactions.</p>

